name: Best Friends Whenever
overview: When their aspiring scientist friend Barry's invention goes awry, best friends Shelby and Cyd gain the power to leap forward and backward in time whenever they want – and sometimes when they don't. Now, they experience the twists and turns of friendship and must decide between fixing mistakes in the past or catching a glimpse of the future. While Barry and his assistant, Naldo, try to figure out how to replicate time travel for themselves, Cyd and Shelby use their newfound power to navigate high school life and Shelby's mischievous twin brothers, Bret and Chet.

episodes.name: A Time to Travel
episodes.overview: Best friends Shelby and Cyd gain the unpredictable power to travel back and forth in time when one of their friend Barry's science inventions goes awry. With their newfound power, the teen besties try to fix the mishaps that spoiled Shelby's plans to ask her crush Cameron out to the school dance.

episodes.name: A Time to Cheat
episodes.overview: When Cyd and Shelby are having trouble studying for a difficult history test, they decide to jump ahead in time and nab the test questions. Meanwhile, Barry and Naldo find themselves in a hair-raising situation when they try to figure out how to make Barry’s invention replicate time travel.

episodes.name: A Time to Say 'Thank You'
episodes.overview: When Cyd tries to plan a special thank you for the Marcus family, Shelby steps in to help with hulu dancers, a rock band and jugglers and everything somehow leads to a big misunderstanding and a huge kitchen disaster.

episodes.name: A Time to Jump and Jam
episodes.overview: Cyd and Shelby travel back to relive one of their favorite memories from middle school, but the moment winds up being totally different than what they both remembered. Now, they begin to question everything that happened on that particular day.

episodes.name: A Time to Rob and Slam
The Butterscotch Effect
episodes.overview: When Cyd and Shelby attempt to change the past so that Barry can meet his childhood science hero, they travel to a period where Naldo and Barry are rock musicians instead of scientists.

episodes.name: Shake Your Booty
episodes.overview: When the girls travel back to the 70's for help on a report, they land right in the middle of a turf battle between punk and disco kids.

episodes.name: Back to the Future Lab
episodes.overview: Cyd and Shelby discover a major clue to the future lab memory and it is somehow tied to Barry's Science mentor Janet Smythe, who also employs Shelby's dad.

episodes.name: Cyd and Shelby Strike Back (1)
episodes.overview: When the girls discover inventor and GDD CEO Janet Smythe is behind the future lab, they decide to fight back and travel to the past to stop Janet from starting the corporation. Their plan seems to work until they realize they also stopped other major events from happening in their lives, including them living together and Barry and Marci falling for each other.

episodes.name: The Girls of Christmas Past
episodes.overview: Things spin out of control when Cyd travels back to Christmas the year before to try and figure out the perfect gift for Shelby. Meanwhile, Barry and Naldo's Winter Wonderland experiment sparks an elf war with Bret and Chet leading the charge.

episodes.name: A Time to Double Date
episodes.overview: Cyd and Shelby use time travel to attend two different events on the same night; the plan backfires when they meet boys at both events.

episodes.name: Jump to the '50's
episodes.overview: When Shelby's adventurous Grandma Rita comes to visit, the girls learn time travelers were responsible for setting up Shelby's grandparents and they jump to the 1950s to investigate.

episodes.name: Diesel Gets Lost in Time
episodes.overview: Diesel swallows a time travel tracker and disappears; Shelby and Cyd hurry to track him down before he's lost forever.

episodes.name: Fight The Future: Part 2
episodes.overview: When Janet unexpectedly invites herself over to Shelby's for dinner, the girls use the opportunity to find out what she knows about time travel.

episodes.name: Fight The Future: Part 3
episodes.overview: While Janet tries to uncover the secret behind time travel, the girls decide they need to take her down once and for all!

episodes.name: Princess Problems
episodes.overview: A princess named Daisy has come through the time rift from the 16th century and finds herself at Cyd and Shelby's school.

episodes.name: Worst Night Whenever
episodes.overview: Bret and Chet worry about their sixth grade dance; haunted by the nemories of their own experience, Cyd and Shelby go back in time for a do-over.

episodes.name: Epic Girl's Day
episodes.overview: The girls decide to take Daisy on an official "Epic Girl's Day" at the mall since she might be here longer than expected.

episodes.name: Girl Code
episodes.overview: Barry is too busy to help Shelby build her website so she takes matters in to her own hands; Cyd and Naldo win a boat and try to hide it in the backyard.

episodes.name: Derby Little Secret
episodes.overview: Cyd and Shelby watch roller derby against Astrid's wishes; they find out Shelby's mom has been lying.

episodes.name: Night of the Were-Diesel
episodes.overview: When Cyd tries to protect Diesel from Barry’s wolf serum experiment, she accidentally gets the serum on herself and turns into a menacing werewolf. Now Shelby must try and figure out how to get her best friend back before the she-wolf destroys their high school’s Halloween carnival.

episodes.name: Working Nine to Fudge
episodes.overview: Shelby and Cyd get their first jobs at a fudge kiosk at the mall, but the job is not all that Shelby thought it would be.

episodes.name: The Christmas Curse
episodes.overview: Shelby and Cyd encourage a homesick Daisy to incorporate a festive 16th-century tradition into their annual Christmas party.
